Outsourcing the Sales Force

<div align="left">BREAKING THE TABOO?  
Sales Outsourcing has become one of the fastest 
growing areas of the BPO (business process 
outsourcing) market, cornering 15%, with a 30% 
annual growth rate. 

Find out why - and 
how - more 
companies are outsourcing their sales force (once 
considered an "uber-core" sacred cow) at our Sales
 
Outsourcing Microsite (http://5m8.net/hj.9gw?t=yubbic8un.e.9t374854a.kp9d778p2.44170&p=http%3A%2F%19nh7.ea99vm0oc3y.com%l3x3h7e80.883%3Fpage%3D02b%2FSFmicro%ah2jgd7.n4t3%26nonav%3Dfalse).  

